{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cdb23f4719","title":"给来子文\"的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a55a37fc5f","index":0,"year":1936,"month":8,"day":14,"articleId":"cdb23f4719"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"80a44bd8ca","type":"paragraph","text":"给来子文\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cdb23f4719"},{"id":"edcb23cfb3","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年8月14日）子文先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cdb23f4719"},{"id":"f85a2edfb9","type":"paragraph","text":"十年分快，国事全非，救亡图存，惟有复归于联合战线。前次董健吾兄来，托致邮意，不知已达左右否？弟等频年三呼时，希望南京当局改变其对外对内方针，目前虽有若干端倪，然大端仍旧不变，甚难于真正之联合抗日","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cdb23f4719"},{"id":"9d54ded7f0","type":"paragraph","text":"先生邦国闻人，时有抗日绪论，甚佩甚佩！深望竿头更进，起为首倡，排序卖国贼汉好，恢复贵党一九二七年以前孙中山先生之革命精神，实行联俄联共农工三大政策，则非惟救国，亦以自救。寇深锅驱，情切婴鸣，风雨同舟，愿闻明教。勿此布廉，不尽欲言！顺颂公绥","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cdb23f4719"},{"id":"9624597bcd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cdb23f4719"},{"id":"17ac37fea5","type":"paragraph","text":"一九三六年八月十四日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cdb23f4719"},{"id":"654f533de3","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]宋子文（1894—1971），广东文昌（今属海南省）人，国民党英美派代表，当时任国民党政府全国经济委员会主席、中国银行董事长。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cdb23f4719"},{"id":"0e8406fcc4","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]董健吾（1892-1970），江苏青浦（今属上海市）人，当时是中国共产党党员，公开身份是收师，在上海等地从事秘密工作。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cdb23f4719"}],"page":{"id":"258005b6d8","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cdb23f4719","start":72,"end":72}}}},"__N_SSG":true}